{"tid":1834044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老公給36萬年終　老婆驚呆！","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:48:05.000Z","uid":209657,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aee5a1e38e5ca87260c0acdc0f9e5da82deb60f6","tid":1834044,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/22/2373469-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2F2373469-XXL.jpg&h=313c5a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豬年就要結束，許多公司行號也在近期發放年終或紅包，感謝員工在過去一年的付出。就有一名全職媽媽去刷簿子的時候，發現丈夫轉了36萬給她當年終獎金，讓她又驚又喜。而篇貼文也讓許多網友看了相當羨慕，甚至還有網友開玩笑地說：「貼出來是要讓其他家庭鬧革命喔！」<br />\n<br />\n一名女網友在臉書社團「爆廢公社」貼出了一張存摺內頁的照片，只見1月21日有一筆轉帳存款，共36萬，還有一句「老婆辛苦了」的5字備註。這也讓原PO看了相當驚訝。回家詢問老公後，老公只告訴她：「全職媽媽更辛苦，當然也有年終。」這也讓原PO感動地直呼：「謝謝老公！」<br />\n<br />\n許多網友看到原PO從老公那邊領到36萬年終後，也相當羨慕，目前這篇貼文也有1.8萬人按讚，還有1千多則留言，「別人的老公怎麼都那麼棒」、「看看別人、看看自己，我要哭了」、「已羨慕」，還有許多媽媽留言比慘，「我連3600都沒有」、「3600？我連36都沒看到」，也有不少女網友紛紛留言標註另一半，「希望下次我也能領到這麼多XD」，還有人知足地表示，「我老公的年終全都拿出來貢獻家庭開銷了，也是很棒啦」。"},{"pid":"12764c658f53382890a8c46371cd25ddacc0a7b0","tid":1834044,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:17:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=677228&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=mainpage&amp;fbclid=IwAR18pvFTuHzFtvYft07QUlmYuEVTYYJ7YL7icqkke3NgqInG48aOudB2tnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D677228%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dmainpage%26fbclid%3DIwAR18pvFTuHzFtvYft07QUlmYuEVTYYJ7YL7icqkke3NgqInG48aOudB2tnI&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=de9bdcd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D677228%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dmainpage%26fbclid%3DIwAR18pvFTuHzFtvYft07QUlmYuEVTYYJ7YL7icqkke3NgqInG48aOudB2tnI&h=83cf6203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=677228&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=mainpage&amp;fbclid=IwAR18pvFTuHzFtvYft07QUlmYuEVTYYJ7YL7icqkke3NgqInG48aOudB2tnI</a>"},{"pid":"41ae4948066fa310418a067f40ff2265e0adaa79","tid":1834044,"uid":55924,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾做壞規矩 <br />\n比完台妹36萬分分都有老王"},{"pid":"702f895a2d129011f81ebf227a2ace03ebcddf6e","tid":1834044,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"41ae4948066fa310418a067f40ff2265e0adaa79","tid":1834044,"uid":55924,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾做壞規矩 <br />\n比完台妹36萬分分都有老王"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"等一下..."},{"pid":"27a4d6052fc42de8da252d81369998261be2865e","tid":1834044,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"36萬屌一世，除笨有精"},{"pid":"9d43c6d9af829564011323eeb0c74a387b81722b","tid":1834044,"uid":28263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"702f895a2d129011f81ebf227a2ace03ebcddf6e","tid":1834044,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"41ae4948066fa310418a067f40ff2265e0adaa79","tid":1834044,"uid":55924,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾做壞規矩 <br />\n比完台妹36萬分分都有老王"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"等一下..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"我有老公..."},{"pid":"e68bd7eff0cbfad14d8785f0e5ad7757748c0c0b","tid":1834044,"uid":321374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"下年冇50萬準備跪玻璃"},{"pid":"1d2656644c41d4f50e857d91cd3e332319f7677e","tid":1834044,"uid":78995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d43c6d9af829564011323eeb0c74a387b81722b","tid":1834044,"uid":28263,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"702f895a2d129011f81ebf227a2ace03ebcddf6e","tid":1834044,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":